column2: SELECT TOP # SELECT  o.objid,o.ra,o.dec, s.bestobjid, s.z as redshift, s.class as specClass,  o.petroRad_r,o.petroRadErr_r, o.u,o.g,o.r,o.i,o.z,o.petroMagErr_u,o.petroMagErr_g,  o.petroMagErr_r,o.petroMagErr_i,o.petroMagErr_z,  e.Flux_OIII_#,e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#,e.Flux_NII_#_Err,  e.Flux_Ha_#,e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.Flux_Hb_#,e.Flux_Hb_#_Err,  o.petroR5#_r, o.petroR5#Err_r, o.petroR9#_r, o.petroR9#Err_r FROM PhotoObj AS o  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = o.objid  JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE  s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND  o.u-o.r <= # AND  o.r-o.i <= # AND  o.r-o.z<=# AND  o.g-o.r >= o.r-o.i+# AND  o.u-o.r >= #*(o.r-o.z)
